The paper deals with algorithms for planarity testing and planar embedding, which are fundamental problems in computational geometry and graph theory. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms), followed by cs.CG (Computational Geometry) and cs.DM (Discrete Mathematics). The paper also uses concepts from complexity theory, which suggests categories such as cs.CC (Computational Complexity) and cs.GT (Computer Science and Game Theory) as possible options.
